Text: Exclusive InvitationMultex Investor Member Youre invited to an exclusive preview of Multex Investors NEW Personal Finance Channel at mktgmitxie Use this new resource of timely reliable information and tools to help you make more informed decisions about your personal finances on such topics as mortgages insurance and retirement As a Multex Investor member you can take advantage of this great new content before its made available to the public Simply visit mktgmitxie to Ask an expert for advice on mortgages insurance or retirement planning read informative educational articles and case studies use the Broker Centers objective tool to find out which brokerage firm best fits your needs and more At the Personal Finance Channel you can also learn from the strategies other investors have tried The channel presents reallife case studies that examine important life events like planning for retirement distributions deciding whether to take a home equity loan or a home equity line of credit and planning for longterm care Were excited to bring you this new Personal Finance Channel and we hope that it enhances your experience on Multex Investor Click here mktgmitxie Sincerely Robin Spindel Director of Marketing Multexcom PS As always we greatly appreciate your feedback and input Feel free to contact us anytime at mail to
